In a message dated 2/15/03 12:35:39 AM Central Standard Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> "Good luck"said Hydras"I trust in you, Maxima..."

Glancing about her at the new found technology with a wicked grin. She would 
have fun with this. 

Then looking up at him with her clear blue optics as they sparkled. Ready for 
action & it was about bloody damn time! 

She dropped her her 'knees' before him, crossing her arm over her chest in a 
salute as she had done many times long ago, slightly bowing her head, " I 
shall not fail you, Hydras," in her mind she remembered stating this to 
Megatron a couple times, kneeling in the same manner. 

Then looking up at him in a wicked grin. This would be fun.

--part1_4b.2acf6e0f.2b7f3d6b_boundary
